[30;1m616 | [0m[35m### Added[0m
[30;1m617 | [0m[35m- New SHACL Advanced Spec Features![0m
[30;1m618 | [0m[35m- All NodeExpressions can now be used in SHACL Rules[0m
[30;1m619 | [0m[35m  - Focus Node (sh:this)[0m
[30;1m620 | [0m[35m  - FilterShape (sh:filterShape)[0m
